OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry, with
OL,6,Flong clear periods for most. Though
OL,7,Fgenerally cloudy across the northeast.
OL,8,FPatchy frost and fog forming in the
OL,9,Fnorth, whilst the south will remain
OL,10,Frather breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FMorning fog clearing to
OL,13,Fleave a sunny day for most. Perhaps a
OL,14,Ffew showers moving into the far
OL,15,Fsouthwest of England. Windy in the
OL,16,Fsouth. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
